{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-custom-post-tsx","path":"/posts/2021/2021-04-03-Concurrently_using_Concurrently/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"cf965bf9-9eeb-552e-bfa0-92ed0c5cb0ce","fields":{"slug":"/2021/2021-04-03-Concurrently_using_Concurrently/"},"html":"<h1>Concurrently 사용하여 express 서버와 webpack 동시 실행</h1>\n<h2>Concurrently 모듈</h2>\n<p><strong>> 설치</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 현재 작업하고 있는 프로젝트만 적용시키고 싶을 때</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> i <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--save</span> concurrently\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 글로벌 설치</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> i <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-g</span> concurrently</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>> 사용법</strong><br>\npackage.json에서 script 부분에 key명을 명시 후, 값에는 concurrently를 앞에 명시해주고 뒤에 실행시키고 싶은 명령어를 쓰기</p>\n<ul>\n<li>예시\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"scripts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">\"start\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"concurrently \\\"nodemon app.js\\\" \\\"webpack -w\\\"\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>위의 “scripts”에 “start”라는 명령을 등록함. 실행 시 <code class=\"language-text\">npm start</code></li>\n<li>실행화면<br>\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/33610315/113480648-685d8580-94d0-11eb-9f65-6fad461754f3.png\" width=\"700\"></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3>참고자료</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/concurrently\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">npmjs : concurrently</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://bin-repository.tistory.com/138\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">[Concurrently] 서버와 클라이언트 동시에 실행시키기!</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"[Library] Concurrently를 사용하여 동시실행","summary":null,"date":"2021.04.03.","categories":["Library"],"options":null,"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/c4d1a539f77981f65fb49eb9438b7262/b25f9/background_library.png","srcSet":"/static/c4d1a539f77981f65fb49eb9438b7262/9f1c5/background_library.png 213w,\n/static/c4d1a539f77981f65fb49eb9438b7262/bb852/background_library.png 426w,\n/static/c4d1a539f77981f65fb49eb9438b7262/b25f9/background_library.png 852w","sizes":"(min-width: 852px) 852px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/c4d1a539f77981f65fb49eb9438b7262/afa7f/background_library.webp 213w,\n/static/c4d1a539f77981f65fb49eb9438b7262/4b6dc/background_library.webp 426w,\n/static/c4d1a539f77981f65fb49eb9438b7262/08c68/background_library.webp 852w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 852px) 852px, 100vw"}]},"width":852,"height":852}},"publicURL":"/static/c4d1a539f77981f65fb49eb9438b7262/background_library.png"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2021/2021-04-03-Concurrently_using_Concurrently/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1642645631","2183628444","3096950251","3590156278","3949884163","77750267","884297919"]}